{"tid":1470234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾670車長聯署促港鐵回應三訴求","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:36:11.000Z","uid":64181,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3fc127250a8497c3faf24c2b03bcf3733f35261e","tid":1470234,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:36:22.000Z","msg":"港鐵員工今日會到港鐵九龍灣總部請願，遞交9條路線逾670名列車車長的聯署信，並向管理層提出訴求，要求在星期五之前作公開回應，否則或拒絕執行職務。<br />\n<br />\n列車車長不滿警方近日在港鐵站附近或站內發射催淚彈，以及上月元朗暴力襲擊事件後救援速度緩慢，但港鐵對警方的行動只表示非常遺憾，未有譴責或阻嚇。<br />\n<br />\n他們提出3項訴求，要求港鐵強烈譴責警方各種影響鐵路安全的行動，促請警方重視鐵路及車站安全，避免使用大規模武力如橡膠子彈、催淚彈等，以免傷及無辜。同時要求港鐵確實肩負起保障員工與乘客的責任，自主調配或更改列車與車站運作，而非盲目地配合警方要求。還要求公司徹底清洗、消除所有依附在車站、列車及通風系統中的有毒粒子，並在完成有關工作前，向員工及乘客派發可過濾有機氣體的口罩，減低受傷風險並恢復市民乘搭港鐵的信心。<br />\n<br />\n他們要求港鐵周五前回應，否則會考慮以保障人身安全為由，拒絕執行職務。"},{"pid":"00498265bd5bc8eba32411b0226efb74f2e990ee","tid":1470234,"uid":32786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f034df923147f13f9b7f1e47881991617bdb85e8","tid":1470234,"uid":177811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:23:08.000Z","msg":"他們要求港鐵周五前回應，否則會考慮以保障人身安全為由，拒絕執行職務。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c45cc1b88669817383f0bbe0d5aec2f23978a05","tid":1470234,"uid":37986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:25:59.000Z","msg":"仲有元朗射催淚彈上路軌一定要講!!!"},{"pid":"b9c98543896d7f496fb8b580354ce52427f99cd8","tid":1470234,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"374ac77a54879d74915e233071a4b9c89a538b06","tid":1470234,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:28:12.000Z","msg":"做返齣好戲啦車長<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n班高層話之你哋死呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634395236784b294bde9bed6b23e1b8dae31f7df","tid":1470234,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rOQhrma.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrOQhrma.jpg&h=ca5a75c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4334ea916cb11f08e9074e6fc2d8dcdce941ecaf","tid":1470234,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:35:52.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"af3f6f646590597c7217ecc69d09a0ffee705c9c","tid":1470234,"uid":227588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:36:11.000Z","msg":"嘥氣，臨門一腳又係跪低。<br />\n<br />\n唔該，俾一次要我跌眼鏡啦。"}]}